# Hostnames allowed through the private-network firewall.
# One hostname per line. Lines starting with # are comments.
# These are resolved at container startup and added as iptables ACCEPT rules
# BEFORE the private-network DROP rules.
#
# Place your actual file at ~/.config/jailoc/allowed-hosts
#
# Example: internal MCP servers
# document-search.asistent.ftxt.dszn.cz
# mcp.ai.iszn.cz
